title: Episode 293: Poop, Burns, & Cousins (Feat. Page Kennedy)
itunes:title: Episode 293: Poop, Burns, & Cousins (Feat. Page Kennedy)
description:
Rapper/Actor, Page Kennedy joins the ladies of Lip Service to promote his new album “Page.” Page gets open and honest when discussing surgery for weight loss, that time he got burnt after contracting multiple STDs, that messy night during anal sex, and much more. Enjoy!


Instrumentals produced by PERFXN & Big Len Music
